      <section eId="sec_7_1_531">
        <num>7-1-531</num>
        <content>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1919, p. 135, art. 13, §§ 1, 2; Code 1933, §§ 13-1401, 13-1402; Ga. L. 1973, p. 278, § 1; Code 1933, § 41A-2402, enacted by Ga. L. 1974, p. 705, § 1; Ga. L. 2007, p. 502, § 5/SB 70; Ga. L. 2018, p. 214, § 10/HB 780; Ga. L. 2021, p. 323, § 8/HB 111.)</p>
          <p>The 2018 amendment,
      effective May 3, 2018, in subparagraph (a)(2)(B), substituted "Unless the article or bylaws require a greater vote, the" for "The" at the beginning, substituted "a majority" for "two-thirds" near the middle, substituted "a majority" for "at least two-thirds" in the middle, and added the proviso at the end; and substituted "Whenever a meeting of shareholders is called for the purpose of taking action on a plan, the notice for such meeting" for "The notice" at the beginning of paragraph (a)(3). See Editor's notes for applicability.</p>
          <p>The 2021 amendment,
      effective July 1, 2021, redesignated former paragraph (a)(3) as present paragraph (a)(4) and added paragraph (a)(3).</p>
        </content>
      </section>
